item.title: About me
item.description: Sujit is an experienced software development professional played multiple roles in application and product development. Sujit has more than 12 years of experience on coding, designing and architecting solutions, leading and mentoring development teams across geographies. Sujit architected, design and developed reliable backend systems by using Core Java, Spring framework, REST API and other open source software technologies ecosystem in Service Oriented and Micro Services Architecture. I am a continuous learner and having passion (also curious) for learning latest technologies and work on the personal projects to apply my learning.
